PRODUCT     CoA [CPD:C00010];
            biochanin A 7-O-(6-O-malonyl-beta-D-glucoside) [CPD:C12625]
COMMENT     The 6-position of the glucose residue of formononetin can also act as acceptor; some other 7-O-glucosides of isoflavones, flavones and flavonols can also act, but more slowly.
